description: Lists the operations performed by AWS Systems Manager for SAP.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: The filters of an operation. (dict) --- A specific result obtained by specifying the name, value, and operator. The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values The operator for the filter.

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive.

nested_params.name: Value
nested_params.description: The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values.
